==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Soybean oil
<hw>Soy"bean oil</hw> <pr>(soi"b⟦emac⟧n` oil)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>an oil obtained from the soybean (<spn>Glycine max</spn>), rich in
protein, fats, sterols, and phospholipids, used as a food and in paints
and varnishes and in various industrial applications; -- called also
<altname>soya oil</altname>. It is also used in preparing the sauce
called <prod>soy</prod> or <prod>soy sauce</prod>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Soyle</ent>⟦br⟧
